<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٢٧١ -<span class="c5"> قَالَ:</span> وَكَانَتْ بِنْتُ عُتْبَةَ تُرْقِصُ ابْنَهَا عُتْبَةَ بْنَ أَبِي سُفْيَانَ وَتَقُولُ:<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[البحر الرجز]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>إِنَّ بُنَيَّ مِنَ الرِّجَالِ حَمْسٌ ... كَرِيمُ أَصْلٍ وَكَرِيمُ نَفْسٍ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>لَيْسَ بِوَجَّابِ الْفُؤَادِ نِكْسِ<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>